{"tid":1499743,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[路透社] 立陶宛、拉脫維亞紀念Baltic Way，並與香港示威者連結","createTime":"2019-08-23T23:51:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-24T01:46:12.000Z","uid":64191,"like":39,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"29b925b0715472c54265d0e3bc8d50ded84febf4","tid":1499743,"uid":64191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T23:51:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://reut.rs/2Z8SXMW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Freut.rs%2F2Z8SXMW&d=iLyAB%2BOE6twWPMF9W2uC6s5Q2JFdPMmcxM5Tq6mQO7A%3D&h=93c2a53f\" target=\"_blank\">https://reut.rs/2Z8SXMW</a><br />\n<br />\n大致翻譯：<br />\n<br />\n星期五，在香港組成人鏈的同時，立陶宛也在首都Vilnius紀念Baltic Way 30周年，有12000名國民拉起象徵性人鏈。隊伍中，有人帶香港及西藏旗，向香港的人鏈活動致敬。<br />\n<br />\n其中一名受訪者，30年前有參加Baltic Way，表示人鏈是「<span style=\"color: red;\">告訴暴君我們不在恐懼，將要擁抱自由。</span>」認為這個宗旨激勵了香港人追求自由及權利。<br />\n<br />\n立陶宛總統在出席另一場與拉脫維亞合辦既活動時，表示「<span style=\"color: red;\">香港人的福利、和平及繁榮係我地共同既目標」&ldquo;The welfare, peace and prosperity of Hong Kong&rsquo;s people is a goal we all share.&rdquo;</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">路透社引述立陶宛一名國會議員，表示當日有少數中國人舉起中國國旗，企圖擾亂立陶宛人既活動時，被警察到場阻止，其中有兩名中國人被拘捕</span>。"},{"pid":"e43d9aa932eb9d6b6509519a6ca9f7fdafb08c15","tid":1499743,"uid":223664,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T23:53:35.000Z","msg":"有兩個中國人被捕<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62f328aa977f3eba72b66e63ef94a784ef97a6c1","tid":1499743,"uid":113183,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T23:54:59.000Z","msg":"我有睇段片<br />\n個幾隻戰螂鬧立陶宛人係混蛋"},{"pid":"0e16b20b4a7928981139cd40fabfeda2f9f1e28b","tid":1499743,"uid":64191,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"62f328aa977f3eba72b66e63ef94a784ef97a6c1","tid":1499743,"uid":113183,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T23:54:59.000Z","msg":"我有睇段片<br />\n個幾隻戰螂鬧立陶宛人係混蛋"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T23:55:58.000Z","msg":"移民去人地到，鬧人地國民同核心價值係混蛋<img src=